<p>► Modern and elegant hotel with a great position<br />► In the heart of the city, close to Piazza Venezia<br />► Good buffet breakfast<br />► Panoramic rooftop terrace with spectacular views over Rome</p>
<p>This smart hotel is conveniently located close to Piazza Venezia and within easy reach off all the main attractions. There is a great selection of shops, cafés, bars and restaurants nearby as well as good connections by bus to Termini train station. Facilities include lounge and bar, breakfast room, reading room, TV room and lift. The panoramic terrace, with breathtaking views over the city, is a highlight and the perfect place to relax after a busy day sightseeing. All the spacious rooms have shower or bath, telephone, satellite TV, minibar, hairdryer, air-conditioning and safe (at reception).<br />Single rooms are available at a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Inghams PLUS</strong><br />► Basket of fruit for honeymoon couples<br />► Free Berlitz guide book</p>
